%^YELLOW%^Skill: Influence

%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^A player's influence skill indicates their ability to convince others of a belief or path of action. It involves both persuasion, intimidation, bluffing, depending which may be called upon at a time.

%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Stat basis: %^WHITE%^charisma
%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Current areas of influence: %^WHITE%^vendor pricing, followers and/or henchmen

%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Related helpfiles: %^WHITE%^skills
